{
  "id": 76,
  "nameSimple": "Al-Insan",
  "nameArabic": "الانسان",
  "versesCount": 31,
  "revelationPlace": "madinah",
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 5592,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "verseKey": "76:1",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": " هَلْ أَتَىٰ عَلَى ٱلْإِنسَـٰنِ حِينٌ مِّنَ ٱلدَّهْرِ لَمْ يَكُن شَيْـًٔا مَّذْكُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 578,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101601,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Has there [not] come upon man a period of time when he was not a thing [even] mentioned?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752305,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "人确实经历一个时期，不是一件可以记念的事物。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5593,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "verseKey": "76:2",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّا خَلَقْنَا ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ مِن نُّطْفَةٍ أَمْشَاجٍ نَّبْتَلِيهِ فَجَعَلْنَـٰهُ سَمِيعًۢا بَصِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 578,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101613,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, We created man from a sperm-drop mixture<sup foot_note=230245>1</sup> that We may try him; and We made him hearing and seeing.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752306,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已用混合的精液创造人，并加以试验，将他创造成聪明的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5594,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "verseKey": "76:3",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّا هَدَيْنَـٰهُ ٱلسَّبِيلَ إِمَّا شَاكِرًا وَإِمَّا كَفُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 578,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101625,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, We guided him to the way, be he grateful or be he ungrateful.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752307,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已指引他正道，他或是感谢，或是辜负。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5595,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "verseKey": "76:4",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّآ أَعْتَدْنَا لِلْكَـٰفِرِينَ سَلَـٰسِلَا۟ وَأَغْلَـٰلًا وَسَعِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 578,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101629,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, We have prepared for the disbelievers chains and shackles and a blaze.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752308,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已为不信者预备许多铁链、铁圈和火狱。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5596,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "verseKey": "76:5",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ ٱلْأَبْرَارَ يَشْرَبُونَ مِن كَأْسٍ كَانَ مِزَاجُهَا كَافُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 578,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101631,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, the righteous will drink from a cup [of wine] whose mixture is of Kāfūr,<sup foot_note=230246>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752309,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "善人们必得饮含有樟脑的醴泉，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5597,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "verseKey": "76:6",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "عَيْنًا يَشْرَبُ بِهَا عِبَادُ ٱللَّهِ يُفَجِّرُونَهَا تَفْجِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101633,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "A spring of which the [righteous] servants of Allāh will drink; they will make it gush forth in force [and abundance].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752310,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "即安拉的众仆所饮的一道泉水，他们将使它大量涌出。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5598,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "verseKey": "76:7",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يُوفُونَ بِٱلنَّذْرِ وَيَخَافُونَ يَوْمًا كَانَ شَرُّهُۥ مُسْتَطِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101635,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "They [are those who] fulfill [their] vows and fear a Day whose evil will be widespread.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752311,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们履行誓愿，并畏惧灾难普降日。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5599,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "verseKey": "76:8",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَيُطْعِمُونَ ٱلطَّعَامَ عَلَىٰ حُبِّهِۦ مِسْكِينًا وَيَتِيمًا وَأَسِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101637,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And they give food in spite of love for it<sup foot_note=230249>1</sup> to the needy, the orphan, and the captive,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752312,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们为喜爱安拉而赈济贫民、孤儿、俘虏。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5600,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "verseKey": "76:9",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّمَا نُطْعِمُكُمْ لِوَجْهِ ٱللَّهِ لَا نُرِيدُ مِنكُمْ جَزَآءً وَلَا شُكُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101639,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[Saying], \"We feed you only for the face [i.e., approval] of Allāh. We wish not from you reward or gratitude.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752313,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "“我们只为求得安拉的恩赐和喜悦，而赈济你们，我们不望你们的报酬和感谢。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5601,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "verseKey": "76:10",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّا نَخَافُ مِن رَّبِّنَا يَوْمًا عَبُوسًا قَمْطَرِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101602,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, We fear from our Lord a Day austere and distressful.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752314,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我们的确畏惧从我们的主发出的严酷的一日。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5602,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "verseKey": "76:11",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَوَقَىٰهُمُ ٱللَّهُ شَرَّ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلْيَوْمِ وَلَقَّىٰهُمْ نَضْرَةً وَسُرُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101603,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "So Allāh will protect them from the evil of that Day and give them radiance and happiness",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752315,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "故安拉将为他们防御那日的灾难，并赏赐他们光华和快乐。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5603,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "verseKey": "76:12",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَجَزَىٰهُم بِمَا صَبَرُوا۟ جَنَّةً وَحَرِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101604,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And will reward them for what they patiently endured [with] a garden [in Paradise] and silk [garments].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752316,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他将因他们的坚忍而以乐园和丝绸报酬他们。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5604,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "verseKey": "76:13",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "مُّتَّكِـِٔينَ فِيهَا عَلَى ٱلْأَرَآئِكِ ۖ لَا يَرَوْنَ فِيهَا شَمْسًا وَلَا زَمْهَرِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101605,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[They will be] reclining therein on adorned couches. They will not see therein any [burning] sun or [freezing] cold.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752317,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们在乐园中，靠在床上，不觉炎热，也不觉严寒。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5605,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "verseKey": "76:14",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَدَانِيَةً عَلَيْهِمْ ظِلَـٰلُهَا وَذُلِّلَتْ قُطُوفُهَا تَذْلِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101606,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And near above them are its shades, and its [fruit] to be picked will be lowered in compliance.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752318,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "乐园的荫影覆庇着他们，乐园的果实，他们容易采摘。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5606,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "verseKey": "76:15",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَيُطَافُ عَلَيْهِم بِـَٔانِيَةٍ مِّن فِضَّةٍ وَأَكْوَابٍ كَانَتْ قَوَارِيرَا۠",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101607,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And there will be circulated among them vessels of silver and cups having been [created] clear [as glass],",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752319,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "将有人在他们之间传递银盘和玻璃杯--",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5607,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "verseKey": "76:16",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "قَوَارِيرَا۟ مِن فِضَّةٍ قَدَّرُوهَا تَقْدِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101608,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Clear glasses [made] from silver of which they have determined the measure.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752320,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "晶莹如玻璃的银杯，他们预定每杯的容量。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5608,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "verseKey": "76:17",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَيُسْقَوْنَ فِيهَا كَأْسًا كَانَ مِزَاجُهَا زَنجَبِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101609,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And they will be given to drink a cup [of wine] whose mixture is of ginger",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752321,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们得用那些杯饮含有姜汁的醴泉，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5609,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "verseKey": "76:18",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 231,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "عَيْنًا فِيهَا تُسَمَّىٰ سَلْسَبِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101610,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[From] a fountain within it [i.e., Paradise] named Salsabeel.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752322,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "既乐园中有名的清快泉。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5610,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "verseKey": "76:19",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "۞ وَيَطُوفُ عَلَيْهِمْ وِلْدَٰنٌ مُّخَلَّدُونَ إِذَا رَأَيْتَهُمْ حَسِبْتَهُمْ لُؤْلُؤًا مَّنثُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101611,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "There will circulate among them young boys made eternal. When you see them, you would think them [as beautiful as] scattered pearls.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752323,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "许多长生不老的少年，轮流着服侍他们。当你看见那些少年的时候，你以为他们是些散漫的珍珠。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5611,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "verseKey": "76:20",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَإِذَا رَأَيْتَ ثَمَّ رَأَيْتَ نَعِيمًا وَمُلْكًا كَبِيرًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101614,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And when you look there [in Paradise], you will see pleasure and great dominion.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752324,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "当你观看那里的时候，你会看见恩泽和大国。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5612,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "verseKey": "76:21",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "عَـٰلِيَهُمْ ثِيَابُ سُندُسٍ خُضْرٌ وَإِسْتَبْرَقٌ ۖ وَحُلُّوٓا۟ أَسَاوِرَ مِن فِضَّةٍ وَسَقَىٰهُمْ رَبُّهُمْ شَرَابًا طَهُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101615,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Upon them [i.e., the inhabitants] will be green garments of fine silk and brocade. And they will be adorned with bracelets of silver, and their Lord will give them a purifying drink.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752325,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们将穿着绫罗锦缎的绿袍，他们将享受银镯的装饰，他们的主，将以纯洁的饮料赏赐他们。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5613,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "verseKey": "76:22",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 516,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ هَـٰذَا كَانَ لَكُمْ جَزَآءً وَكَانَ سَعْيُكُم مَّشْكُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101616,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "[And it will be said], \"Indeed, this is for you a reward, and your effort has been appreciated.\"",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752326,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "（将对他们说）“这确是你们的报酬，你们的劳绩是有报酬的。”",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5614,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "verseKey": "76:23",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّا نَحْنُ نَزَّلْنَا عَلَيْكَ ٱلْقُرْءَانَ تَنزِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101617,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, it is We who have sent down to you, [O Muḥammad], the Qur’ān progressively.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752327,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我确已将《古兰经》零星地降示你，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5615,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "verseKey": "76:24",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَٱصْبِرْ لِحُكْمِ رَبِّكَ وَلَا تُطِعْ مِنْهُمْ ءَاثِمًا أَوْ كَفُورًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101618,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "So be patient for the decision of your Lord and do not obey from among them a sinner or ungrateful [disbeliever].",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752328,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "故你应当忍受你的主的判决。你不要顺从他们中任何犯罪的人，或孤恩的人。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5616,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "verseKey": "76:25",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱذْكُرِ ٱسْمَ رَبِّكَ بُكْرَةً وَأَصِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 579,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101619,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And mention the name of your Lord [in prayer] morning and evening",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752329,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你应当朝夕记念你的主的尊名，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5617,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "verseKey": "76:26",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمِنَ ٱلَّيْلِ فَٱسْجُدْ لَهُۥ وَسَبِّحْهُ لَيْلًا طَوِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 580,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101620,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And during the night prostrate to Him and exalt [i.e., praise] Him a long [part of the] night.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752330,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "夜里，你应当以小部份时间向他叩头，以大部份时间赞颂他。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5618,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "verseKey": "76:27",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ يُحِبُّونَ ٱلْعَاجِلَةَ وَيَذَرُونَ وَرَآءَهُمْ يَوْمًا ثَقِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 580,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101621,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, these [disbelievers] love the immediate and leave behind them<sup foot_note=230256>1</sup> a grave Day.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752331,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这等人的确是爱好现世，而忽视未来的严重的一日",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5619,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "verseKey": "76:28",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "نَّحْنُ خَلَقْنَـٰهُمْ وَشَدَدْنَآ أَسْرَهُمْ ۖ وَإِذَا شِئْنَا بَدَّلْنَآ أَمْثَـٰلَهُمْ تَبْدِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 580,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101622,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "We have created them and strengthened their forms, and when We will, We can change their likenesses with [complete] alteration.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752332,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我创造了他们，并使他们的体格坚实。如果我意欲，我将以像他们一样的人代替他们。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5620,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "verseKey": "76:29",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّ هَـٰذِهِۦ تَذْكِرَةٌ ۖ فَمَن شَآءَ ٱتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِۦ سَبِيلًا",
      "pageNumber": 580,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101623,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, this is a reminder, so he who wills may take to his Lord a way.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752333,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这确是教诲，谁愿意觉悟，谁可以选择一条通达他的主的道路。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5621,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "verseKey": "76:30",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ كَانَ عَلِيمًا حَكِيمًا",
      "pageNumber": 580,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101626,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And you do not will except that Allāh wills. Indeed, Allāh is ever Knowing and Wise.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752334,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "除安拉意欲外，你们决不意欲。安拉是全知的，是至睿的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5622,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "verseKey": "76:31",
      "hizbNumber": 58,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 232,
      "rukuNumber": 517,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يُدْخِلُ مَن يَشَآءُ فِى رَحْمَتِهِۦ ۚ وَٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ أَعَدَّ لَهُمْ عَذَابًا أَلِيمًۢا",
      "pageNumber": 580,
      "juzNumber": 29,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 101627,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He admits whom He wills into His mercy; but the wrongdoers - He has prepared for them a painful punishment.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752335,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他使他所意欲的人，入在他的慈恩中。至于不义的人，他已为他们预备了痛苦的刑罚。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}